Merge: 0d7895a 5399094
David Reveman <davidr@novell.com>	2006-09-21

    Merge branch 'master' of git+ssh://git.freedesktop.org/git/xorg/app/compiz

David Reveman <davidr@novell.com>	2006-09-21

    Remove compiz.desktop, it shouldn't be in repository.

