Merge: 43046fc 47f5066
Dan Winship <danw@twelve-monkeys.boston.ximian.com>	2006-07-20

    Merge branch 'master' of git+ssh://git.freedesktop.org/git/xorg/app/compiz
    
    Conflicts:
    
plugins/compiz.schemas.in.in           
plugins/gconf-dump.c           
